<heading id="D0A21F3FB25AFF9BECC2E93BFE59FBD2" bold="true" box="[151,486,1086,1111]" fontSize="10" level="2" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" reason="2">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BECC2E93BFE59FBD2" bold="true" box="[151,486,1086,1111]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
Monophyly of 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BED10E93BFE59FBD2" authorityName="sensu Christenhusz &amp; Chase" authorityYear="2014" box="[325,486,1086,1111]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Tectariaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Tectarioideae">Tectarioideae</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C34FFBD8B25AFF9BECC2E967FCC3FA66" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BEAA853B25AFF9BECC2E967FCC3FA66" blockId="7.[151,1437,1086,1507]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
Our results are in line with the suggestion that 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEECBE967FB91FBFE" authority="sensu Holttum (1947)" authorityName="sensu Holttum" authorityYear="1947" box="[670,1070,1122,1147]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Tectariaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Tectarioideae">
Tectarioideae 
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEF6EE966FCC6FBFF" box="[827,889,1123,1146]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">sensu</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4D5A2B25AFF9BEF2AE967FB91FBFE" author="Holttum, R. E." box="[895,1070,1122,1147]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="123 - 158" refId="ref11105" refString="Holttum, R. E. (1947) A revised classification of leptosporangiate ferns. Journal of the Linnean Society, Botany 53: 123 - 158. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1095 - 8339.1947. tb 02554. x" type="journal article" year="1947">Holttum (1947)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
are polyphyletic. The placement of 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BECE3E983FE8BFB1A" box="[182,308,1158,1183]" class="Dothideomycetes" family="Micropeltidaceae" genus="Cyclopeltis" kingdom="Fungi" order="Microthyriales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BECE3E983FE8BFB1A" box="[182,308,1158,1183]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Cyclopeltis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in subfamily 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BED84E983FD15FB1A" baseAuthorityName="Christenhusz &amp; Chase" baseAuthorityYear="2014" box="[465,682,1158,1183]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Lomariopsidaceae" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Lomariopsidoideae">Lomariopsidoideae</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4D5A2B25AFF9BEEEEE983FC3EFB1A" author="Smith, A. R. &amp; Pryer, K. M. &amp; Schuettpelz, E. &amp; Korall, P. &amp; Schneider, H. &amp; Wolf, P. G." box="[699,897,1158,1183]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="705 - 731" refId="ref13243" refString="Smith, A. R., Pryer, K. M., Schuettpelz, E. Korall, P., Schneider, H., Wolf, P. G. (2006) A classification of extant ferns. Taxon 55: 705 - 731. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.2307 / 25065646" type="journal article" year="2006">
Smith 
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEF50E982FC81FB1A" box="[773,830,1158,1183]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">et al.</emphasis>
2006
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4D5A2B25AFF9BEFD9E983FB0CFB1A" author="Schuettpelz, E. &amp; Pryer, K. M." box="[908,1203,1158,1183]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="1037 - 1050" refId="ref13127" refString="Schuettpelz, E. &amp; Pryer, K. M. (2007) Fern phylogeny inferred from 400 leptosporangiate species and three plastid genes. Taxon 56: 1037 - 1050. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.2307 / 25065903" type="journal article" year="2007">Schuettpelz &amp; Pryer 2007</bibRefCitation>
) is supported by our analyses, as is the inclusion of 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEDA1E9AEFDE6FB47" authorityName="Holttum &amp; Edwards" authorityYear="1986" box="[500,601,1195,1218]" genus="Dryopsis" kingdom="Plantae" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEDA1E9AEFDE6FB47" box="[500,601,1195,1218]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Dryopsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEEC5E9AEFD58FB47" box="[656,743,1195,1218]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dryopteridaceae" genus="Ctenitis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEEC5E9AEFD58FB47" box="[656,743,1195,1218]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Ctenitis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEF59E9AFFC6FFB46" box="[780,976,1194,1219]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dryopteridaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Dryopteridoideae">Dryopteridoideae</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4D5A2B25AFF9BEF8AE9AFFBC0FB46" author="Li, C. - X. &amp; Lu, S. - G." box="[991,1151,1194,1219]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="503 - 515" refId="ref11885" refString="Li, C. - X. &amp; Lu, S. - G. (2006) Phylogenetic analysis of Dryopteridaceae based on chloroplast rbcL sequences. Acta Phytotaxonomica Sinica 44 (5): 503 - 515. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1360 / aps 050081" type="journal article" year="2006">Li &amp; Lu 2006</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4D5A2B25AFF9BE8DEE9AFFA8CFB46" author="Liu, H. - M. &amp; Zhang, X. - C. &amp; Chen, Z. - D." box="[1163,1331,1194,1219]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="789 - 798" refId="ref11938" refString="Liu, H. - M., Zhang, X. - C. &amp; Chen, Z. - D. (2007) Polyphyly of the fern family Tectariaceae sensu Ching: insights from cpDNA sequence data. Science in China C, Life Sciences 50 (6): 789 - 798. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1007 / s 11427 - 007 - 0099 - 9" type="journal article" year="2007">
Liu 
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BE8ECE9AEFB4DFB46" box="[1209,1266,1194,1219]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">et al.</emphasis>
2007
</bibRefCitation>
). Indeed, 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BECC2E9CAFF41FB63" authorityName="Holttum &amp; Edwards" authorityYear="1986" box="[151,254,1231,1254]" genus="Dryopsis" kingdom="Plantae" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BECC2E9CAFF41FB63" box="[151,254,1231,1254]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Dryopsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has already been merged with 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEE30E9CAFC37FB62" authority="(Zhang 2012)" baseAuthorityName="Zhang" baseAuthorityYear="2012" box="[613,904,1230,1255]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dryopteridaceae" genus="Dryopteris" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEE30E9CAFD5EFB63" box="[613,737,1231,1254]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Dryopteris</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4D5A2B25AFF9BEEA5E9CBFC3FFB62" author="Zhang, L. - B." box="[752,896,1230,1255]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="17 - 27" refId="ref13919" refString="Zhang, L. - B. (2012) Reducing the fern genus Dryopsis to Dryopteris and the systematics and nomenclature of Dryopteris subgenus Erythrovariae section Dryopsis (Dryopteridaceae). Phytotaxa 71: 17 - 27." type="journal article" year="2012">Zhang 2012</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, although this may cause 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BE8E6E9CAFA90FB63" baseAuthorityName="Zhang" baseAuthorityYear="2012" box="[1203,1327,1231,1254]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dryopteridaceae" genus="Dryopteris" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BE8E6E9CAFA90FB63" box="[1203,1327,1231,1254]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Dryopteris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
not to be monophyletic (
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4D5A2B25AFF9BED14E9F7FD3AFA8E" author="Christenhusz, M. J. M. &amp; Chase, M. W." box="[321,645,1266,1291]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="571 - 594" refId="ref10237" refString="Christenhusz, M. J. M. &amp; Chase, M. W. (2014) Trends and concepts in fern classification. Annals of Botany 113: 571 - 594." type="journal article" year="2014">Christenhusz &amp; Chase 2014</bibRefCitation>
). 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEECDE9F6FD4FFA8F" box="[664,752,1267,1290]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dryopteridaceae" genus="Ctenitis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEECDE9F6FD4FFA8F" box="[664,752,1267,1290]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Ctenitis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(including 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEF21E9F6FC4FFA8F" authorityName="R.E.Holttum" authorityYear="1984" box="[884,1008,1267,1290]" genus="Ataxipteris" kingdom="Plantae" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEF21E9F6FC4FFA8F" box="[884,1008,1267,1290]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Ataxipteris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) forms a lineage with 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BE8A4E9F7FA23FA8E" authorityName="Tardieu-Blot" authorityYear="1955" box="[1265,1436,1266,1291]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dryopteridaceae" genus="Pseudotectaria" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BE8A4E9F7FA23FA8E" box="[1265,1436,1266,1291]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Pseudotectaria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and both are deeply embedded in 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEE62E813FCB0FAAA" box="[567,783,1302,1327]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dryopteridaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Dryopteridoideae">Dryopteridoideae</taxonomicName>
, even though these three genera share morphological characteristics with 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEDDDE83FFD97FAD6" authorityName="sensu Holttum" authorityYear="1947" box="[392,552,1338,1363]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Tectariaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Tectarioideae">Tectarioideae</taxonomicName>
and were associated with it previously. 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BE859E83FFB28FAD6" box="[1036,1175,1338,1363]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dryopteridaceae" genus="Pleocnemia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BE859E83FFB28FAD6" box="[1036,1175,1338,1363]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Pleocnemia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which was placed in 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BECC2E85BFE9BFAF2" authorityName="sensu Holttum" authorityYear="1947" box="[151,292,1374,1399]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Tectariaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Tectariaceae</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4D5A2B25AFF9BED05E85BFD96FAF2" author="Smith, A. R. &amp; Pryer, K. M. &amp; Schuettpelz, E. &amp; Korall, P. &amp; Schneider, H. &amp; Wolf, P. G." box="[336,553,1374,1399]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="705 - 731" refId="ref13243" refString="Smith, A. R., Pryer, K. M., Schuettpelz, E. Korall, P., Schneider, H., Wolf, P. G. (2006) A classification of extant ferns. Taxon 55: 705 - 731. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.2307 / 25065646" type="journal article" year="2006">
Smith 
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEDC9E85AFE6AFAF2" box="[412,469,1374,1399]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">et al.</emphasis>
(2006)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4D5A2B25AFF9BEE34E85BFC34FAF2" author="Christenhusz, M. J. M. &amp; Zhang X. - C. &amp; Schneider, H." box="[609,907,1374,1399]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" pagination="7 - 54" refId="ref10376" refString="Christenhusz, M. J. M., Zhang X. - C. &amp; Schneider, H. (2011) A linear sequence of extant families and genera of lycophytes and ferns. Phytotaxa 19: 7 - 54." type="journal article" year="2011">
Christenhusz 
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEEA8E85AFC88FAF2" box="[765,823,1374,1399]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">et al.</emphasis>
(2011)
</bibRefCitation>
, is here shown to belong to 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BE89BE85BFA27FAF2" box="[1230,1432,1374,1399]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Dryopteridaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Dryopteridoideae">Dryopteridoideae</taxonomicName>
, agreeing with other recent studies (e.g. 
<bibRefCitation id="EFC4D5A2B25AFF9BEE32E887FCA4FA1E" author="Liu, H. - M. &amp; He, L. - J. &amp; Schneider, H." box="[615,795,1410,1435]" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" refId="ref12094" refString="Liu, H. - M., He, L. - J., Schneider, H. (2014) Towards the natural classification of tectarioid ferns: Confirming the phylogenetic relationships of Pleocnemia and Pteridrys (eupolypods I). Journal of Systematics and Evolution. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1111 / jse. 12073" type="book" year="2014">
Liu 
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEECDE886FD6CFA1E" box="[664,723,1410,1435]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">et al.</emphasis>
2014
</bibRefCitation>
). With the exclusion of these genera, 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BE881E887FACFFA1E" authorityName="sensu Holttum" authorityYear="1947" box="[1236,1392,1410,1435]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Tectariaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Tectarioideae">Tectarioideae</taxonomicName>
are monophyletic and are composed of 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEE79E8A3FD09FA3A" box="[556,694,1446,1471]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Nephrolepidaceae" genus="Arthropteris" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEE79E8A3FD09FA3A" box="[556,694,1446,1471]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Arthropteris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEE91E8A3FC93FA3A" box="[708,812,1446,1471]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Tectariaceae" genus="Pteridrys" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEE91E8A3FC93FA3A" box="[708,812,1446,1471]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Pteridrys</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEF69E8A3FC64FA3A" authorityName="Holttum" authorityYear="1986" box="[828,987,1446,1471]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Tectariaceae" genus="Triplophyllum" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEF69E8A3FC64FA3A" box="[828,987,1446,1471]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Triplophyllum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BEFBFE8A3FBD5FA3A" box="[1002,1130,1446,1471]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Tectariaceae" genus="Hypoderris" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BEFBFE8A3FBD5FA3A" box="[1002,1130,1446,1471]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Hypoderris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BE8F7E8A2FB41FA3B" box="[1186,1278,1447,1470]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Tectariaceae" genus="Tectaria" kingdom="Animalia" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BE8F7E8A2FB41FA3B" box="[1186,1278,1447,1470]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Tectaria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. We were not able to sample 
<taxonomicName id="4C55D3D0B25AFF9BED6AE8CEFE5CFA67" box="[319,483,1483,1506]" class="Polypodiopsida" family="Tectariaceae" genus="Aenigmopteris" kingdom="Plantae" order="Polypodiales" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9217441B25AFF9BED6AE8CEFE5CFA67" box="[319,483,1483,1506]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">Aenigmopteris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, so its placement remains uncertain.
</paragraph>
